reviewText: I like the movie because I have seen it previously. But I couldn't get the dvd to play in any of the players at my house. It was a faulty disc. So I returned it. I ended up buying a brand new one at Walmart and it was cheaper.
love the movie, this is a fictional book of a real person. Drew Barrymore, Ben Kingly, Helen Bonham Carter are great.
This is my favorite Cinderella story! I watch it over and over again.
I love this movie. By the third or fourth time viewing it, I decided it was worth owning.
definitely a ladies movie~happily ever after!!
